This is a javascript package to turn python into javascript

# import
how to import: import jscript

# packages required

# sample code

```python
import jscript as js
js.console.log("hi")
js.console.warn("daw")
js.console.error("daw")
js.console.count(6)
prompt("dawdawd") #this one has bugs
#thats all for now
```
